'''大麻'''（{{Lang-es|Cannabis、Marijuana}}）是一种使用[[大麻属|大麻属]]植物制成的[[藥物|藥物]]，在[[医用大麻|医疗合法化]]的国家被视为醫療用藥，是使用雌性[[大麻属|大麻]]的花與毛狀體晾晒製成的。主要分為[[寻常大麻|寻常大麻(Sativa)]]（{{lang|la|''Cannabis sativa''}}）、[[印度大麻|印度大麻(Indica)]]（{{lang|la|''Cannabis indica''}}）和结合两者特点的[[杂交大麻|杂交大麻(Hybrid)]]（或称混合大麻，{{lang-en|hybrid cannabis}}）三種[[大麻品種|栽培品種]]。其主要作用于精神方面，主要的成份為[[四氢大麻酚|四氢大麻酚]]（tetrahydrocannabinol，缩写THC），而大麻亦含有超過423種已知化合物<ref name="Russo2013">{{cite book|author=Ethan B Russo|title=Cannabis and Cannabinoids: Pharmacology, Toxicology, and Therapeutic Potential|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=qH-2Lj9x7L4C&pg=PP28|year=2013|publisher=Routledge|isbn=978-1-136-61493-4|page=28|access-date=2018-04-08|archive-date=2021-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210207120501/https://books.google.com/books?id=qH-2Lj9x7L4C&pg=PP28|dead-url=no}}</ref>，其中包括至少65种其他[[大麻素|大麻素]]<ref>{{cite book|last1=Newton|first1=David E.|title=Marijuana : a reference handbook|date=2013|publisher=ABC-CLIO|location=Santa Barbara, Calif.|isbn=9781610691499|page=7|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=iWMf95ze8QEC&pg=PA7}}</ref>，例如[[大麻酚|大麻酚]]（cannabinol，簡稱CBN）、[[大麻二酚|大麻二酚]]（cannabidiol，簡稱CBD），它們所產生的感官影響與四氫大麻酚所產生的精神影響有明顯的差異<ref name="pmid19124693">{{cite journal|author=Fusar-Poli P, Crippa JA, Bhattacharyya S, ''et al.''|title=Distinct effects of {delta}9-tetrahydrocannabinol and Cannabidiol on Neural Activation during Emotional Processing|journal=Archives of General Psychiatry]|volume=66|issue=1|pmid=19124693|doi=10.1001/archgenpsychiatry.2008.519|url=http://archpsyc.ama-assn.org/cgi/pmidlookup?view=long&pmid=19124693|accessdate=2009-09-26|date=January 2009}}{{dead link|date=2017年12月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。Marijuana一词是指草藥形式製成的大麻，包括成熟的雌株花、葉、莖，而Hashish（[[哈希什|哈希什]]）則是指大麻樹脂，一種濃縮大麻的方式<ref name="urlTypes of Cannabis Available in the United Kingdom">{{cite web | url = http://www.idmu.co.uk/can.htm | title = Types of ''Cannabis'' Available in the United Kingdom (UK) | author = Matthew J. Atha (Independent Drug Monitoring Unit) | access-date = 2012-01-03 | archive-date = 2021-02-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210207120553/http://www.idmu.co.uk/can.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

