使用大麻后通常会产生多种心理和生理上的反应，比如[[欣快感|欣快感]]和兴奋感、感官意识变化、[[食欲|食欲]]增强<ref name=NIH2016>{{cite web|title=DrugFacts: Marijuana|url=https://www.drugabuse.gov/publications/drugfacts/marijuana|website=National Institute on Drug Abuse|access-date=19 April 2016|date=March 2016|archive-date=2016-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160417153128/https://www.drugabuse.gov/publications/drugfacts/marijuana|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://adai.uw.edu/marijuana/factsheets/appetite.htm |title=Marijuana: Factsheets: Appetite |publisher=Adai.uw.edu |access-date=2013-07-12 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303181518/http://adai.uw.edu/marijuana/factsheets/appetite.htm |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。在吸入后数分钟，食用后30至60分钟内起效<ref name=NIH2016/><ref name=Ri2010/>，效果持续2至6小时<ref name=Ri2010>{{cite book|last1=Riviello|first1=Ralph J.|title=Manual of forensic emergency medicine : a guide for clinicians|date=2010|publisher=Jones and Bartlett Publishers|location=Sudbury, Mass.|isbn=9780763744625|page=41|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=keng9ELAE2IC&pg=PA41|access-date=2018-04-08|archive-date=2017-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170318224346/https://books.google.com/books?id=keng9ELAE2IC&pg=PA41|dead-url=no}}</ref>。短期副作用可能包括：短期记忆力下降、口腔干燥、运动机能受损、红眼、[[偏执|偏执]]或[[焦虑|焦虑]]感<ref name=NIH2016/><ref name="NLMNIH">{{cite web |url=https://www.nlm.nih.gov/medlineplus/ency/article/000952.htm |title=Marijuana intoxication: MedlinePlus Medical Encyclopedia |publisher=Nlm.nih.gov |access-date=2013-07-12 |archive-date=2013-07-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130704123904/http://www.nlm.nih.gov/medlineplus/ency/article/000952.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Crippa JA, Zuardi AW, Martín-Santos R, Bhattacharyya S, Atakan Z, McGuire P, Fusar-Poli P | title = Cannabis and anxiety: a critical review of the evidence | journal = Human Psychopharmacology | volume = 24 | issue = 7 | pages = 515–23 | date = October 2009 | pmid = 19693792 | doi = 10.1002/hup.1048 }}</ref>。长期滥用大麻会导致[[大麻成瘾|大麻成瘾]]，自青少年时期开始长期使用则可能导致[[心智|心智]]能力降低，受孕期间长期服用可能导致儿童行为问题<ref name=NIH2016/>。有研究发现使用大麻和患神经疾病风险有较强关联<ref name=Leweke2016rev>{{cite journal | vauthors = Leweke FM, Mueller JK, Lange B, Rohleder C | title = Therapeutic Potential of Cannabinoids in Psychosis | journal = Biological Psychiatry | volume = 79 | issue = 7 | pages = 604–12 | date = April 2016 | pmid = 26852073 | doi = 10.1016/j.biopsych.2015.11.018 | url = https://www.researchgate.net/publication/285044085_Therapeutic_Potential_of_Cannabinoids_in_Psychosis | access-date = 2018-04-08 | archive-date = 2019-12-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191213133113/https://www.researchgate.net/publication/285044085_Therapeutic_Potential_of_Cannabinoids_in_Psychosis | dead-url = no }}</ref>，但其因果关系仍有争议<ref name="doi:10.1007/s11920-015-0657-y">{{cite journal | vauthors = Ksir C, Hart CL | title = Cannabis and Psychosis: a Critical Overview of the Relationship | journal = Current Psychiatry Reports | volume = 18 | issue = 2 | pages = 12 | date = February 2016 | pmid = 26781550 | doi = 10.1007/s11920-015-0657-y }}</ref>。

